article.headline: Moss' 23 lead Radford over Purdue Fort Wayne 69-56
article.description: — Jarvis Moss scored 23 points as Radford beat Purdue Fort Wayne 69-56 on Tuesday night.
article.linkText: Moss' 23 lead Radford over Purdue Fort Wayne 69-56
article.story: DAYTONA BEACH, Fla. -- — Jarvis Moss scored 23 points as Radford beat Purdue Fort Wayne 69-56 on Tuesday night. Moss had three steals for the Highlanders (6-2). Truth Harris scored 12 points, going 4 of 5 and 3 of 3 from the free-throw line. Jalen Jackson led the Mastodons (4-3) in scoring, finishing with 23 points. Rasheed Bello added 11 points for Purdue Fort Wayne. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
